public class U3duExpression<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Statement<T>

A class for expressions and their evaluation. It is not directly capable of handling compound operators assignments. The direct usage of this class is discouraged yet kept for advanced features.

Author:
Sylvain Cambon
